<p><span class='hashtag'>#作文模版/大作文</span></p>
<br>
<h1 id="大作文娜拉模版">大作文娜拉模版</h1>
<hr>
<h1 id="第一段">第一段</h1>
<ol start="1"><li>第一句：描述图片
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	It is symbolically illustrated in the cartoon above that…
</li></ul>
<p>	正如上图象征性描述的那样，。。。</p>
<ul><li>	总体描述1句+细节描述1-2句
</li><li>	人物+动作+细节+地点
</li></ul>
<p>	多图：共性+个性</p>
<ul><li>	Below the drawing,there is a caption which say’s “    小标题   ”
</li></ul>
<br>
<ol start="2"><li>总结(凑字数)
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	The author’s real aim is not the picture itself, but to lead us to find what hides behind the picture.
</li></ul>
<p>	作者的真实目的不是图片本身，而是引导我们发现藏在图片背	后的东西</p>
<br>
<hr>
<h1 id="第二段">第二段</h1>
<br>
<br>
<ol start="1"><li>第一句（主旨）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	Undoubtedly ,the purpose of the drawing is to show us that (in face of seemingly insurmountable challenges or predicaments, )is of the utmost significance.
</li></ul>
<p>	毫无疑问，这幅画的目的是告诉我们（在面对看似不可抗拒的	挑战和困境时）是非常重要的。</p>
<ul><li>	Apparently, the drawing symbolically illustrates a not common comical phenomenon in our daily life that 
</li></ul>
<p>	很明显，这幅画象征性的论述了我们日常生活中很普遍的现象</p>
<ol start="2"><li>第二句（承上启下）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	I will present the most convincing two arguments out of many potential explanations for my opinion as follows.
</li></ul>
<p>	在众多可能的解释中，我将提出以下最有说服力的两个论点来	说明我的观点。  </p>
<br>
<h2 id="消极篇">消极篇                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           </h2>
<ol start="3"><li>第三句（解释1）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	To begin with, the reason why people carry out this practice is that they are unaware of the adverse impact of <u>主题词</u>
</li></ul>
<p>	首先，民众作出这种行为的原因是是他们没有意识 <u>主题词</u>	带来的影响。</p>
<ol start="4"><li>第四句（解释2）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	In addition, the impact from surroundings, such as a wicked social atmosphere and imperfect relevant systems, might have resulted in this phenomenon occurring everywhere.
</li></ul>
<p>	此外，由于社会风气恶劣，相关制度不完善等环境的影响，可能导致这种现	象随处可见。</p>
<br>
<h2 id="积极篇">积极篇</h2>
<ol start="3"><li>第三句（解释1）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	Primarily,  those  who  have  the  conduct  awareness  of  (主题词)  are  more  likely  to  win  the recognition from the society in an extensive range.
</li></ul>
<p>	 ⾸先，那些具有 (主题词) ⾏为意识的⼈更有可能赢得社会的	认同。</p>
<ul><li>	To  start  with,  (主题词)  has  a  positive  effect  on  each  and  every  one  of  us,  which  is  agreed  by most people.
</li></ul>
<p>	 ⾸先，绝⼤多数⼈认同(主题词)对我们每个⼈都有着积极作⽤</p>
<ol start="4"><li>第四句（解释2）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	In  addition,  we  have  been  holding  supportive  attitudes  towards  (主题词),  which  is  helpful  for enhancing the public’s proper concepts of social values.
</li></ul>
<p>	并且，我们⼀直以来都保持着对(主题词)的⽀持态度，这有助	于持续强化民众良好的⾏为意识。 </p>
<ul><li>	In addition, as an integral part of all aspects of education,(主题词) has aided in a healthy and progressive advancement in today’s youth. 
</li></ul>
<p>	再者，(主题词)作为当代教育不可缺少的⼀部分，这有助于当	今青少年⾝⼼的健康成长。</p>
<ol start="5"><li>第五句（呼吁，凑字数）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	Therefore,  we  should  always  bear  the  significance  of  (主题词)  in  our  mind  under  any circumstance. 
</li></ul>
<p>	所以，我们在任何情况下都应时刻牢记(主题词)的重要意义。</p>
<p> </p>
<hr>
<h1 id="第三段">第三段</h1>
<ol start="1"><li>第一句（引出措施）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	accordingly, it is imperative for us to take some effective and efficient measures to enhance people’s conscious awareness of ( to avoid this situation ) in our society.
</li></ul>
<p> 		因此，我们迫切需要采取有效措施来提高社会中人们的	意识(去避免这一情况)</p>
<ol start="2"><li>第二句（行动1）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	On the level of individual, we should be highly self-disciplined and avoid the same old mistakes.
</li></ul>
<p>	在个人层面，我们应该高度自律，避免重蹈覆辙。</p>
<ol start="3"><li>第三句（行动2）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	On the level of society, the priority of families and schools is to help the young generation with the establishment of good sense of values.
</li></ul>
<p>	从社会层面来讲，学校和家庭的头等大事是帮助建立年轻人的良好价值观。</p>
<ul><li>	On the level of society, the government should not hesitate to implement appropriate regulations in related to this issue.
</li></ul>
<p>	在社会层面，政府应该毫不犹豫出台这个问题的相关政策。</p>
<ol start="4"><li>第四句（展望未来）
</li></ol>
<ul><li>	only in this way can we achieve success and only in the way can our society become more harmonious to live in.
</li></ul>
<p>	只有这样我们才能获得成功，而且只有这样我们的社会才会变的更加和谐。</p>
<br>
<hr>
